SELECT 
    time_bucket('1 second', ts) AS time_window,
    MAX(value) AS max_value
FROM 
    samples 
WHERE 
    $__timeFilter(ts) 
    AND metric = 'cm_create_book_req_duration'
GROUP BY 
    time_window
